Usage: hiliteFeedthroughNets [-help] <fileName> [<netNameList>]

-help          # Prints out the command usage
<fileName>     # Specifies the net mapping file that was generated during
               # partition feedthrough insertion. (string, required)
<netNameList>  # Specifies the name of the net(s) whose feedthrough path should
               # be highlighted. (string, optional)